20yrs…. Let me say it again, 20 YEARS you’ve fought to be the best version of yourself, to be God’s Warrior & have been the hope image for young men and especially women. I know the real you… in & outside of church you walk with the same type of integrity! Whether you’re dealing with one person or a multitude of individuals, you never treat anyone any differently than you would ever want to be treated. You are truly the standard that many wish they could hold themselves accountable to. 

From gaining your first son and late husband as Angel’s and pushing through, to managing the up’s and down’s in ministry, I’m just glad to say that I’ve seen a true Super Woman in my lifetime. They’ll never be another Boss Queen like you Ma! My love for you is deeper than I can show, but I HAVE to let you know that I’m appreciative of every word you’ve ever spoken to me, and I’ll carry them with me forever🤞🏾 My mommy, The Biggest 💎 I’m proud of you, and I love you!!! Happy Anniversary to 20 years of ministry! 🙏🏾♾
